r_avg_div_yield":0.09,"revenue":8478092800.0,"revenue_per_share":1069.43,"revenue_growth":0.059,"ebitda":1721846016.0,"ebitda_margins":0.20309,"gross_margins":0.38125,"operating_margins":0.18207,"profit_margins":0.17431,"net_income":1477798016.0,"total_cash":6613730816.0,"total_cash_per_share":834.325,"total_debt":0.0,"current_ratio":7.466,"free_cashflow":713340480.0,"return_on_equity":0.1576,"enterprise_value":57550528512.0,"enterprise_to_ebitda":33.424,"enterprise_to_revenue":6.788,"earnings_growth":0.324,"shares_outstanding":7927682.0,"float_shares":1861270.0,"held_pct_insiders":0.76015997,"held_pct_institutions":0.121429995,"beta":-0.195,"fifty_two_week_high":14250.0,"fifty_two_week_low":7301.1,"fifty_day_average":8611.863,"two_hundred_day_avg":10089.484,"recommendation":"none","all_time_high":14250.0,"all_time_low":7301.1,"long_business_summary":"ELANTAS Beck India Limited manufactures and sells specialty chemicals for the electrical insulation and construction industries in India. It operates through two segments, Electrical Insulations, and Engineering & Electronic Resins and Materials. The company provides wire enamels, such as primers, lubricants, and binder varnishes for fiberglass coated conductors; impregnating materials, including insulating varnishes and resins; and flexible electrical insulation materials. It also offers casting and potting compounds comprising casting, potting, and encapsulation of electrical and electronic components, such as auto-electrical components, high-voltage insulators, instrument transformers, etc.; impregnation of high-voltage electrical machine windings; binder resins for glass-fibre filament wound arc chamber tubes; and diamond dotted paper for oil-filled transformers. In addition, the company provides materials for electronic protection, including potting compounds, such as conformal, air drying resistant, rapid process acrylic, waterborne conformal, and silicone coatings; and thermal interface materials. Further, it offers engineering materials, such as construction chemicals comprising a range of resinous construction chemicals for industrial floorings, protective coatings, structural repairs, waterproofing, adhesives, and sealants, as well as specialty epoxy and polyurethane anti-microbial floorings and wall coating systems; and reactive polyamides used in epoxy resins to produce top coats and primers, as well as thermosetting adhesives for a various substrates. The company was incorporated in 1956 and is based in Pune, India. ELANTAS Beck India Limited is a subsidiary of Altana AG."}}